h.kg/1593690\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593690</a><br />\n冷氣機師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n突發 擺脫黑暗 今晚十七區全港商場大合唱 《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1593292\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1593292</a><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n元朗獨立左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好再去Yoho Mall 走唔撚到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一齊推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推到上次各大地區搞手見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n緊急號召重拾笑容正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n擺脫偵探引，還我 開心 活力 創意 朝氣嘅連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n時間定位為<del>2000</del> <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2100</span></span>？<br />\n總之每區手足見唔到搞手搞，淨是需要去返之前個唱榮光個商場見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你唱榮光就是手足<br />\n<br />\n齊齊推爆佢。<br />\n今晚我就要見到榮光。<br />\n同埋全世重點宣傳929反共大遊行同埋101民陣遊行</blockquote>"},{"pid":"c40894a6e6bd67486afe8337eeac159fe63581cd","tid":1594870,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:52:44.000Z","msg":"琴日話我太突發<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日比夠18小時文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d381ba282471a90ff168c78a96a5477d955018aa","tid":1594870,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:53:53.000Z","msg":"聆聽手足意見 晏少少再開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;你班香港人唔好遲到啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"619b244b1adcd6646ef640ea868b30463d9f1734","tid":1594870,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"同時宜佈 <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"col